  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale dataset)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). NOTE: contains W-EP-03 weakener — the primary experimental dataset carries a dataVintage predating the model revision by approximately three weeks; the assessment narrative characterises this revision as non-material without formal re-validation.",
