      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented V&V test suite with version-controlled release notes; configuration management records available for the simulation environment.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 is used under a documented software quality plan. Version control records, regression test suite results, and release notes are archived in the project configuration management system. SQA level 2 requirements met."
