      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via at least one benchmark problem with analytical or manufactured solution.",
      "rationale": "Code verification confirmed against the Taylor–Green vortex and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Observed order of convergence matches theoretical second-order accuracy for the finite-volume discretisation. Verification documentation archived per SQA plan."
