      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at CPB-representative flow rates (2.5–7 LPM) and speeds (2000–4500 RPM) spanning the clinical operating envelope. Blood analog fluid properties match published in vitro hemolysis test standards. Geometric similarity to the subject device confirmed via CAD overlay. Validation activities are assessed as sufficiently relevant to the COU at MRL 2."
    },
