      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal quantification of numerical solver error beyond residual monitoring is not required. All steady-state simulations converged to scaled residuals below 1e-5 for continuity and momentum equations. Solver error factor scoped to level 1 per MRL 2 requirements table."
