      "rationale": "In vitro hemolysis measurements performed on a single representative unit of the predicate device per ASTM F1841. Sample-to-sample variability not formally characterised at MRL 2. Unit-to-unit geometric variation assumed negligible based on manufacturing process capability data."
    },
