    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Validation metrics (GVM = 0.94 for velocity fields; RH MAE = 0.07) satisfy acceptance criteria. The v3r2 model revision (2025-03-17) post-dated the finalisation of the primary hemolysis reference dataset (2025-02-24); the assessment team determined that the turbulence model constant recalibration was not material to hemolysis transport predictions and accepted the existing dataset as sufficient without formal post-revision re-validation. Overall credibility assessment supports use of the CFD model for the stated COU at Medium assurance level.",
